                                   Product Description:

"Magic Summertime" brings together 60 feel-good, singalong, summery tracks that span the years, all the way up to the present. Including classics from the likes of Michael Jackson, Abba, Wham!, Justin Timberlake and Billy Joel along with summer hits from DJ Jazzy Jeff And The Fresh Prince and Ricky Martin, the album will appeal to both the Magic listener but with a cohesive, summery tracklisting, this album will brighten your day, whatever the weather!

                                        ENJOY!
